patthana8.65:1.1: Nasukhasahagataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.65:2.1: Nanasukhasahagataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nanasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.65:3.1: Nasukhasahagatañca nanasukhasahagatañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana8.65:4.1: Hetuyā nava …pe… purejāte āsevane cha …pe… avigate nava.
